author: @waterlily6240
text: jaemin really makes us all fall in love with him all over again through this episode. not only it centers on the sport he professionally contested in and ranked 2nd nationwide, but it also shows his good nature/sportsmanship. we can see the passion and skills he has in the sport and it’s so wonderful to see. yet he also slowly taught the others and tried to make the atmosphere light so everyone could learn in a relaxed manner. he also subtly looked out on the others and very accommodating on their needs throughout the episode. during the hockey game, he could easily win it since he skates the best but he let himself to be laid back and let the other team has a win as well. it’s so fulfilling to finally be able to see what he used to professionally do (a speedskater athlete) while still being the absolute sweetheart that he is towards the others.
